l_1985_05_05/canvas/13/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Bon, Bon soooooooooooir [modulation], bon soir! En attendan the John Giorno baaaaaaaand [echo: baaaand].","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Alan Lord","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/jean_paul_curtay_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/13#t=1699,1712"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/jean_paul_curtay_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/13/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Applause.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Audience","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/jean_paul_curtay_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/13#t=1712,1714"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/jean_paul_curtay_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/13/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Pendent que les techniciens vont defiler le renfilage et vice versa [echo], on va visioner le film de Napoleon Moffat qui s’appelle Framed-d. Qui est originalement un super huite qui a ete transfer a trois–three quarter inch, trois quarts video. C’est un film excellent pis un des meilleures… Pour cinq minutes vous avez le poesie visuel plein de geule, okay?","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Alan Lord","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/jean_paul_curtay_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/13#t=1712,1742"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/jean_paul_curtay_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/13/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Chatter.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Audience","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/jean_paul_curtay_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/13#t=1742,1797"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/jean_paul_curtay_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/13/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Napoleon Moffat’s \"Framed\" starts [piano music].","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Tech","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/jean_paul_curtay_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/13#t=1797,1851"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/jean_paul_curtay_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/13/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Film continues [speech: There are spaces that live between us. The transparency of their names. A terrible tragedy that haunts their walls. A revelation of their fiction. Of something which might of happened but that never really occurred].","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Tech","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/jean_paul_curtay_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_05/canvas/13#t=1851,1875"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi19